<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ResultHub - Home</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        header .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        header nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header nav ul li {
            margin: 0 1rem;
        }

        header nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        header nav ul li a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Main Content */
        main {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .introduction {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .introduction .content {
            max-width: 50%;
            padding-right: 2%;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .introduction .image {
            max-width: 400px;
            flex: 1;
            padding-left: 2%;
        }

        .introduction .image img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* How It Works */
        #how-it-works {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        #how-it-works h2 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .steps {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .step {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            width: 30%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .step h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        footer ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        footer ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin: 0 0.5rem;
        }

        footer ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer ul li a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Media Queries for Mobile and Tablet Responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .introduction {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .introduction .content {
                max-width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
                padding-right: 0;
            }

            .introduction .image {
                max-width: 100%;
                padding-left: 0;
            }

            .steps {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .step {
                width: 80%;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

            header nav ul {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            header nav ul li {
                margin: 0.5rem 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            header .logo {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            header nav ul li a {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .step {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">ResultHub</div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="introduction">
            <div class="content">
                <h1 style="font-size: xx-large;">Welcome to ResultHub</h1>
                <p>ResultHub is your one-stop solution for managing and tracking academic results. 
                    Designed for both students and admins, it provides a seamless platform for 
                    uploading, viewing, and analyzing performance data. 
                    Whether you're a teacher managing class results or a student tracking your progress, 
                    ResultHub simplifies the process with user-friendly tools and a secure interface.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="images/image.png" alt="Digital Dashboard">
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="how-it-works">
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <h3>1. Register</h3>
                    <p>Create an account as a student or an admin to start using ResultHub.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <h3>2. Upload Results</h3>
                    <p>Admins can upload results securely to the system for students to access.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <h3>3. Analyze Performance</h3>
                    <p>Use our tools to view detailed performance analytics and insights.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 ResultHub. All rights reserved.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="#terms">Terms of Service</a></li>
            <li><a href="#support">Support</a></li>
        </ul>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
